name: Netburbia
blurb: An online social game where you can own property, create or join governments and groups, and decorate the map with images you create.

rewards.reward:
1 month subscription of premium membership:
*premium accounts will not be purposely deleted regardless of account inactivity
*can have stock exchanges on owned lots (stock exchanges allow the automatic buying and selling of shares)
*can accept payments for game currency on owned lots via a send currency button
*can enable portals on owned lots (this allows character travel to and from qualified lots that are not adjacent to each other)
*ability for sovereign characters to move prestige on lots they are sovereign over
*ability to takeover sovereignty of adjacent lots if sufficient prestige is available
*increased amount of prestige generation
